title: Roadfever - Wolf Pack
description:
Roadfever - Wolf Pack



Hardrock/ rock/ heavy metal
Releasedate:  2013-11-22
Record Label: Avenue of Allies


Coming from the cold mountains of Switzerland, Roadfever brings their second album, Wolf Pack, now signed to the Avenue of Allies label. Rooted in the Eighties, where many of the members, including female vocalist Stevie "Manou" Pike, began their musical journey, Roadfever plays a mix of classic hard rock and heavy metal.
